title: Schumer’s AI meeting will include top labor and civil rights advocates
description: AFL-CIO Liz Shuler and Leadership Conference on Civil and Human Rights president and CEO Maya Wiley will join top tech executives at the forum.

title: Meta rejects own board’s request to suspend account of Cambodian strongman
description: Meta’s Oversight Board recommended suspending Cambodian leader Hun Sen’s Facebook account after he posted a video advocating violence.

title: What the E.U.’s sweeping rules for Big Tech mean for your life online
description: The European Union’s Digital Services Act put additional limits on Big Tech to protect users online. But does it only help people across the pond?
